data.description: Calling all boutique investors! MUVE | PHL was exclusively enlisted by ownership to advertise for sale this turnkey duplex. This tasteful renovation project is fully occupied and stabilized for a qualified investorâ  s portfolio. With each unit leased for $1,825 the net operating income is $40,800, offering a strong return at a 7% capitalization rate. Located in the buzzing community of Brewerytown, surrounded by development and just steps from the West Girard corridor with all urban amenities tenancy would long for. The building is comprised of two, bi-level units and an expansive rear yard. The first unit is comprised of three (3) bedrooms and two (2) full bathrooms as well as rear yard access. The upper unit holds three (3) bedrooms and two (2) full bathrooms and a large, open living space for entertaining. Contact listing broker for property access as well as full financial details.
